<p>He added: 'They're just about to fall into passionate love making when we hear...' </p>

<p>To which Jennifer's character Linda broke the daydream and asked: 'Hey Brad, do you have any Q-tips?' </p>

<p>Brad's character then had to hide himself and act 'nonchalant', the actor jokingly shook his head and read: 'Wait, just a minute...'</p>

<p>With Jennifer's character replying: 'Oh God, I'm so sorry... I did not know anyone was in here.'</p>

